===評價===
電影於2016年6月24日在美國上映，並獲得負面居多的評價，主要批評其不合理和力道不足的劇情、場面和轉折及非可能性的置入性行銷過多<ref name="IDR Bombs – The Wrap">{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/5-reasons-why-independence-day-resurgence-bombed/|title=5 Reasons Why 'Independence Day: Resurgence' Bombed|last=Doty|first=Meriah|date=June 26, 2016|publisher=The Wrap|accessdate=June 27, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628201957/http://www.thewrap.com/5-reasons-why-independence-day-resurgence-bombed/|archive-date=2016-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|title=Independence Day: Resurgence review|url=https://blewe.com/movies/Independence_Day_Resurgence|publisher=Blewe|accessdate=27 June 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819223657/https://blewe.com/movies/Independence_Day_Resurgence|archivedate=2016年8月19日}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度30%，基於227條評論，平均分為4.4/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/independence_day_resurgence/ |title=Independence Day: Resurgence (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=June 21, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622125225/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/independence_day_resurgence/ |archive-date=2016-06-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分32<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/independence-day-resurgence |title=Independence Day: Resurgence reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=June 21, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621192253/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/independence-day-resurgence |archive-date=2016-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分5.2，負面評價居多。多半批評角色過多且不突出，劇情薄弱混亂，且中國的出現量及重要性被放大太多

